config DTB_BUILTIN
    bool "Enable built-in Device Tree (DTB)"
    depends on !X86_64
    default y
    help
      If enabled, a DTB file will be packaged into the firmware image as a
      built-in blob. If disabled, DTB must be provided by bootloader or
      loaded externally at runtime.